tever you do."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"sesungguhnya"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.67","c":"الْأَبْرَارَ","d":"l-abrāra","e":"orang-orang yang baik"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.64","c":"لَفِي","d":"lafī","e":"benar-benar dalam"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.79","c":"نَعِيمٍ","d":"naʿīmin","e":"kesenangan/kenikmatan"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, the righteous will be in pleasure,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ومن امتزج بحبه حب غير الله تنعم في الآخرة بقدر حبه، إذ يمزج شرابه بقدر من شراب المقربين كما قال تعالى في الأبرار: \" إن الأبرار لفي نعيم \" ثم قال: \" يسقون من رحيق مختوم مسك وفي ذلك فليتنافس المتنافسون ومزاجه من تسنيم عيناً يشرب بها المقربون \" فإذا طاب شراب الأبرار لشوب الشراب الصرف الذي هو للمقربين.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, whoever mixes with his love [hubb] the love of other than Allah, he will enjoy bliss [na'eem] in the Hereafter [Akhirah] to the measure of his love, for his drink is mixed with a measure from the drink of the Brought-Near [al-Muqarrabun], just as Allah, the Exalted, said concerning the Righteous [al-Abrar]: \"Indeed, the Righteous are in bliss,\" then He said: \"They are given to drink of a pure, sealed wine, whose seal is musk—for this let the competitors compete—and whose mixture is of Tasneem, a spring from which drink those brought near.\" Thus, the drink of the Righteous is made pleasant by the admixture of the pure drink which is for those Brought Near.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.42","c":"وَإِنَّ","d":"wa-inna","e":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.99","c":"الْفُجَّارَ","d":"l-fujāra","e":"orang-orang durhaka"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.26","c":"لَفِي","d":"lafī","e":"dalam"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.39","c":"جَحِيمٍ","d":"jaḥīmin","e":"neraka"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, the wicked will be in Hellfire."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.6","c":"يَصْلَوْنَهَا","d":"yaṣlawnahā","e":"mereka masuk kedalamnya"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.96","c":"يَوْمَ","d":"yawma","e":"hari"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.14","c":"الدِّينِ","d":"l-dīni","e":"pembalasan"}],"a":{"g":"They will [enter to] burn therein on the Day of Recompense,"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"dan tidaklah"},{"b":"0.62","h":"1.58","c":"هُمْ","d":"hum","e":"mereka"},{"b":"0.99","h":"2.21","c":"عَنْهَا","d":"ʿanhā","e":"dari padanya"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.92","c":"بِغَائِبِينَ","d":"bighāibīna","e":"dengan gaib/meloloskan diri"}],"a":{"g":"And never therefrom will they be absent."}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.22","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"dan apakah"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.37","c":"أَدْرَاكَ","d":"adrāka","e":"kamu melihat"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.2","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.02","c":"يَوْمُ","d":"yawmu","e":"hari"},{"b":"3.7","h":"6.07","c":"الدِّينِ","d":"l-dīni","e":"pembalasan"}],"a":{"g":"And what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"thumma","e":"kemudian"},{"b":"0.99","h":"1.39","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apakah"},{"b":"2.2","h":"1.74","c":"أَدْرَاكَ","d":"adrāka","e":"kamu melihat"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.04","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.86","c":"يَوْمُ","d":"yawmu","e":"hari"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.97","c":"الدِّينِ","d":"l-dīni","e":"pembalasan"}],"a":{"g":"Then, what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?"}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.2","c":"يَوْمَ","d":"yawma","e":"hari"},{"b":"0.67","h":"1.11","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"tidak"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.73","c":"تَمْلِكُ","d":"tamliku","e":"berdaya/berkuasa"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.14","c":"نَفْسٌ","d":"nafsun","e":"manusia"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.25","c":"لِنَفْسٍ","d":"linafsin","e":"bagi diri/seseorang"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.8","c":"شَيْئًا","d":"shayan","e":"sesuatu/sedikitpun"},{"b":"6.3","h":"10","c":"وَالْأَمْرُ","d":"wal-amru","e":"dan urusan"},{"b":"7.4","h":"11.5","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"pada hari itu"},{"b":"9.5","h":"13.13","c":"لِلَّهِ","d":"lillahi","e":"bagi Allah"}],"a":{"g":"It is the Day when a soul will not possess for another soul [power to do] a thing; and the command, that Day, is [entirely] with Allah."}}}